import { Box, Tab, Tabs } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

function ProductHot() {
  return (
    <Box>
    <Tabs
    indicatorColor='primary'
    >
      <Tab style={{width:"50%"}} label="Discount"/>

     
      <Tab style={{width:"50%"}} label="New Products"/>
      </Tabs>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default ProductHot
